data.description: Wonderful opportunity to be within walking distance to schools, shopping, parks, church's, recreational facilities, entertainment and restaurants. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has a den, that can be used as a 4th bedroom, and a sunroom.  Pergo and wood floors.  Newer air conditioning, windows, dishwasher, furnace, water heater and shed.  Kitchen refrigerator, washer & dryer stay with sale- with no warranties expressed or implied. Property is being sold in it's current condition.  1344 square foot home with an additional 273 garage conversion, according to the assessor, and the porch was converted to a sunroom.  Property needs a little TLC.  Wood stove will be removed before close of escrow.
